{"tid":959869,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鋼筋偷工減料 三豐百貨店倒塌事故","createTime":"2018-12-29T03:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T13:53:49.000Z","uid":12599,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"352021b7ebf02d07b4833d854441c1756546d362","tid":959869,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:07:59.000Z","msg":"三豐百貨店倒塌事故（韓語：삼풍백화점 붕괴 사고／三豊百貨店崩壞事故，英語：Sampoong Department Store Collapse）為韓國大型百貨公司商場倒塌事故，發生於1995年6月29日下午5點52分，當時營業中的三豐百貨大樓開始倒塌，20秒內，5層百貨大樓層層塌陷進地下4層內，共造成502人死亡，937人受傷，財產損失高達2,700億韓元（約等於美金2.16億）。這場災難是韓國在非戰時傷亡最嚴重的災難事故，也曾是全球最嚴重的建築物自行倒塌安全事故，直至2013年孟加拉國薩瓦區大樓倒塌事故。事故現為全世界第二嚴重的建築物自行倒塌災難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QKE5R6QMGAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQKE5R6QMGAw&d=AudTVMWvoZ5SaVOz%2Bgr6JuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=de46006d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QKE5R6QMGAw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E4%B8%89%E8%B1%90%E7%99%BE%E8%B2%A8%E5%BA%97%E5%80%92%E5%A1%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25B1%2590%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2595%2585&d=AudTVMWvoZ5SaVOz%2Bgr6JuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=c902d896\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E4%B8%89%E8%B1%90%E7%99%BE%E8%B2%A8%E5%BA%97%E5%80%92%E5%A1%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85</a><br />\n<br />\n香港膠鐵: 我話ok就ok啦, cut短鋼筋唔代表唔安全, 聽日記得準時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b7564daadd0a62a2f34f5822b5297501217645","tid":959869,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:41:49.000Z","msg":"泡菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n資訊post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj